When asked to write a commit message:

Write a multi-line git commit message for me to enter manually at the command line. Be sure to state in the first line if it is a change in poolparty, statecounter, or both packages. Print it out for me to copy and paste (DO NOT EDIT THIS FILE). It should describe the above changes since the last commit, and should include bullet points. Escape characters as needed for shell compatibility, including `, ', and ".
